-- Manchester United Beats Aston Villa to Win 20th League Title
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-04-22T20:51:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-22/manchester-united-beats-aston-villa-to-win-20th-league-title.html
Manchester United extended its
record number of English soccer championships to 20 with a 3-0
win over Aston Villa.  Robin van Persie  scored a hat trick in the first 33 minutes
at Old Trafford tonight as United captured a 13th Premier League
title in the competition’s 21-year history. The victory,
combined with defending champions Manchester City’s 3-1 loss at
Tottenham yesterday, gives United an unbeatable 16-point lead in
the standings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  